node.text:
Another look at the @cogrid19 posters. Check out my post from yesterday if you missed it! My portion of the grid is representative of finding the beauty in the small, quiet moments during this pandemic. While the last few months have been filled with plenty of frustration and uncertainty, I’ve been trying my best to focus on the good. I’ve tried to settle into this strange new time by enjoying the stillness, noticing the details that may normally be overlooked, and practicing gratitude for all that I have.
